Class GUI

java.lang.Object
GUI
public class GUI
extends java.lang.Object

This class contains the graphical interface and the front-end components of the project. It contains a Project object that contains all the back-end functionality.

See Also:
JButton, JLabel, JTextField, ImageIcon, JFrame, Project

    If there is a file selected, will perform the top-down function on the string in the text field area.
    class  GUI.FileListener
    When performed, will run the project's readFile method, and display the file path in a label in the GUI
    class  GUI.Panel
    This class contains all the graphical components and will initailize them with its constructor.
